+communiqu%c3%a9s+by+t...%22%2c%22ContributorID%22%3a%221%22%2c%22LanguageID%22%3a%22Turkish%22%2c%22CountryID%22%3a%22182%22%2c%22CityID%22%3a%2239%22%2c%22AffiliateID%22%3a%221%22%2c%22PracticeAreaID%22%3anull%2c%22Tags%22%3anull%2c%22CreationDate%22%3a%222018-02-07T22%3a05%3a45.6032291%2b03%3a00%22%2c%22ViewCount%22%3a0%7d%5d%2c%22TestArticlePieces%22%3a%5b%7b%22ID%22%3a%22596911fe-1857-44d2-8f8a-e69bcb80a371%22%2c%22ArticleId%22%3a%229b257d6e-1caa-4cad-a0fd-fe6ad29898e5%22%2c%22Title%22%3anull%2c%22Paragraph%22%3a%22%3cp%3ePerforming+the+annual+corporate+housekeeping+of+your+company+will+bring+various+benefits+for+the+company%2c+its+bodies+and+authorized+individuals.+Though+it+may+be+missed+out+easily+by+the+companies%2c+actually+it+is+easier+to+duly+handle+the+procedures+by+considering+your+effectiveness+and+the+benefits+at+the+end+of+the+day.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eWe+can+simply+count+the+main+trivets+of+the+corporate+housekeeping%2c+as+doing+ordinary+general+assembly+meetings%2c+keeping+updated+your+representation+documents+(%3cem%3ei.e.%3c%2fem%3e+signature+circulars)+and+duly+keeping+the+corporate+books.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3eOrdinary+general+assembly+meetings+and+representation+matters%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eBoth+joint+stock+companies+(%e2%80%9cJSCs%e2%80%9d)+and+limited+liability+companies+(%e2%80%9cLLCs%e2%80%9d)+must+be+held+their+annual+general+assembly+meetings+for+each+year.+As+per+the+Turkish+law%2c+these+ordinary+general+assembly+meetings+must+be+held+within+three+months+following+the+end+of+the+relevant+fiscal+year.+Once+we+consider+that+most+of+Turkish+companies+uses+the+calendar+year+for+their+fiscal+year+period+in+general%2c+we+can+say+that+these+%3cstrong%3ecompanies+must+be+held+their+annual+general+assemblies+for+the+year+of+2017%2c+until+the+end+of+March+2018.%3c%2fstrong%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eIn+general%2c+during+the+ordinary+general+assembly+meetings%2c+annual+activity+reports+and+financial+statements+of+the+company+is+negotiated%2c+audit+reports+are+read+and+the+auditors+are+appointed+and+most+significantly%2c%3cstrong%3e+the+members+of+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+are+released%3c%2fstrong%3e+and+the+new+members+are+appointed+if+the+current+members%e2%80%99+duty+period+is+expired+(or+the+appointment+of+the+new+member(s)+are+approved+if+there+was+an+appointment+by+the+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+due+to+the+change+of+any+member+during+the+relevant+year).%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eTherefore%2c+general+assembly+processes+are+also+good+opportunities+to+negotiate+the+other+outstanding+or+upcoming+issues+of+the+companies%2c+especially+for+the+corporate+requirements+such+as+determination+of+the+authorities%2c+issuance+or+renewal+of+the+authorization+limits+etc.+(such+as+bringing+monetary+limits+or+specifying+the+duty+periods).+These+procedures+are+beyond+the+legal+formalities+only%2c+and+they+should+be+considered+as+the+opportunities+in+order+to+strengthen+the+companies%e2%80%99+standing+with+regard+to+the+corporate+requirements+and+increase+their+effectiveness+in+this+regard%2c+since+performing+these+processes+timely%2c+will+prevent+the+unnecessary+delays+due+to+a+deficiency+of+a+corporate+requirement+by+conducting+the+company%e2%80%99s+commercial+business.+(Think+about+you+just+noticed+three+days+before+the+attendance+date+of+a+very+important+tender%2c+the+duty+period+of+the+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+expired+last+month!)%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3eDuly+keeping+the+corporate+books%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAll+merchants+(even+real+person+merchants)+must+duly+issue+and+keep+their+general+journals+(Tr.+%3cem%3eyevmiye+defteri%3c%2fem%3e)%2c+inventory+books+(Tr.+%3cem%3eenvanter+defteri%3c%2fem%3e)+and+general+ledgers+(Tr.+%3cem%3edefter-i+kebir%3c%2fem%3e).+Additionally%2c+there+are+some+other+mandatory+books+to+be+issued+and+kept+by+the+companies.+For+the+companies+which+are+subject+to+this+article%2c+JSCs+must+also+keep+share+ledger+(Tr.+pay+defteri)%2c+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+resolution+book+(Tr.+%3cem%3ey%c3%b6netim+kurulu+karar+defteri%3c%2fem%3e)+and+general+assembly+meeting+book+(Tr.+%3cem%3egenel+kurul+toplant%c4%b1+ve+m%c3%bczakere+defteri%3c%2fem%3e)+and+LLCs+must+keep+share+ledger+and+general+assembly+meeting+book.+As+it+is+seen%2c+LLCs+do+not+have+to+issue+an+additional+book+for+board+of+managers%e2%80%99+resolutions+(Tr.%3cem%3e+m%c3%bcd%c3%bcrler+kurulu+karar+defteri%3c%2fem%3e)%3b+however%2c+in+case+they+do+not+issue+this+book%2c+their+board+of+managers%e2%80%99+resolutions+must+be+attached+into+their+general+assembly+resolution+book.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAccording+to+Turkish+law%2c+abovementioned+company+books+must+be+issued+at+the+establishment+and+before+starting+to+use+of+them.+However%2c+these+books+are+subject+to+different+closing+or+renewal+certification+periods.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eGeneral+journals%2c+inventory+books+and+general+ledgers+and+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+resolution+book+must+be+certified+for+each+fiscal+year.+Share+ledger+and+general+assemblies%e2%80%99+resolution+book+may+be+continued+to+be+used+in+case+they+have+blank+pages+enough.+In+case+the+pages+of+books+(which+are+subject+to+certification)+are+used%2c+the+companies+must+issue+the+relevant+new+ones+by+making+the+required+certifications+for+such+books.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eGeneral+journals+and+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+resolution+books+must+be+certified+annually+by+the+notary+public+(%3cem%3eclosing+certification%3c%2fem%3e).+General+journals+must+be+certified+until+the+end+of+sixth+month+of+the+following+fiscal+year+and+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+resolution+book+must+be+certified+until+the+end+of+first+month+of+the+following+fiscal+year.+The+rule+is+the+same+for+the+board+of+managers%e2%80%99+resolution+book%2c+if+it+is+issued.+To+clarify%2c+we+can+say+that+for+most+Turkish+companies+(which+uses+the+calendar+year+for+their+fiscal+year+period)%2c+%3cstrong%3ethe+general+journals+must+be+certified+for+the+year+of+2017%2c+until+the+end+of+June+2018+and+the+board+of+directors%e2%80%99+resolution+books+must+have+their+closing+certification+for+the+year+of+2018+until+the+end+of+January+2019.%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3eConclusion%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eConsidering+the+procedural+requirements+of+the+legislation+will+bring+more+benefits+by+saving+your+time+and+minimizing+your+corporate+risks+during+your+commercial+activities+in+addition+to+protect+the+companies%e2%80%99+good+standing+in+the+eye+of+the+law.+On+the+other+hand%2c+it+should+not+be+forgotten+that+authorized+individuals+of+the+companies+are+liable+for+their+management+activities+at+the+companies.%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%22%2c%22ImageUrl%22%3a%22%22%2c%22ImagePosition%22%3a0%7d%2c%7b%22ID%22%3a%2241fd50b4-0a85-4a39-a4e2-5fce2a49c9c0%22%2c%22ArticleId%22%3a%221%22%2c%22Title%22%3anull%2c%22Paragraph%22%3a%22%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eFollowing+the+incident+of+a+Russian+Su-24+jet+being+downed+by+Turkish+F-16+fighters+on+24+November+2015+causing+the+Russian+aircraft+crash+in+the+Bayirbucak+region+of+northern+Syria%2c+Russia+imposed+a+series+of+economic+measures+and+sanctions+against+Turkey.+The+first+step+in+this+direction+was+a+decree+prohibiting+Turkish+products+along+with+other+sanctions%2c+approved+by+the+President+of+Russia+Vladimir+Putin+on+28+November+2015.+With+this+presidential+decree+(numbered+583)%2c+the+legal+ground+was+prepared+for+economic+embargos+on+Turkey+and+Turkish+goods+and+services.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eFollowing+this+decree%2c+the+Russian+Government+fleshed+out+the+decree%e2%80%99s+commercial+sanctions+with+an+Executive+Order+on+30+November+2015+(numbered+1296).+On+28+December+2015%2c+some+amendments+were+introduced+to+the+previously+approved+decree%2c+indicating+the+specifics+and+scope+of+previously+determined+sanctions.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eMajor+sectors+that+are+affected+by+the+commercial+sanctions+are+construction%2c+tourism+and+hotel+management%2c+architecture%2c+engineering-technical+projects+(technical+tests%2c+research%2c+analysis)+and+woodworking.+Additionally%2c+from+1+January+2016%2c+it+is+also+prohibited+for+companies+that+are+subject+to+Turkish+legislation+and%2for+controlled+by+Turkish+citizens+to+do+business+with+the+Russian+government+or+municipalities%2c+regardless+of+the+sector+these+companies+operate+in.+A+public+statement+by+the+Russian+government+explains+that+the+sanctions+in+the+Executive+Order+do+not+apply+to+projects+contracted+before+1+January+2016.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eAs+of+the+date+of+writing%2c+the+types+of+the+sanctions%2c+limitations+and+prohibitions+applied+by+Russia+against+Turkey+include%3a%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eImports+of+Agricultural+Goods%2c+Raw+Materials+and+Food+Products+Prohibited%3a%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eThe+Russian+government+imposed+an+embargo+on+Turkish+products%2c+especially+fruits%2c+vegetables%2c+flowers%2c+chicken%2c+turkey+and+salt.+In+this+regard%3a%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eFruits%3a%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%26nbsp%3b%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cul%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0805+10-+Orange%2c+fresh+or+dried%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0805+20-+Tangerine+(all+kinds+and+hybrids)%2c+fresh+or+dried%2c%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0806+10-+Grapes%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0808+10-+Apple%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0808+30-+Pear%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0809+10-+Apricot%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0809+30-+Peach+and+nectarine%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0809+40-+Plum+and+sloe%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0810+10-+Strawberry%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3c%2ful%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eVegetables%3a%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cul%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0207+14-+Tomato%2c+fresh+or+cooled%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0207+27-+Onion%2c+fresh+or+cooled%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0704+10-+Cauli+and+broccoli%2c+fresh+or+cooled%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0707+00-+Cucumber+and+gherkin%2c+fresh+or+cooled%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3c%2ful%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eBirds%3a%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cul%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0207+14-+Pieces+and+giblets+of+chicken%2c+frozen%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0207+27-+Pieces+and+giblets+of+turkey%2c+frozen%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3c%2ful%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eOthers%3a%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cul%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+0603+12-+Clove%2c+fresh%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3cli%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eGTIP+2501+00-+Salt+and+pure+sodium+chloride%3b+sea+water%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fli%3e%3c%2ful%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eTurkish+Companies+Prohibited+From+Carrying+Out+Certain+Activities+in+Russia%3a%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eIn+certain+operation+fields%2c+prohibitions+and+limitations+apply+to+the+activities+of+companies+and+organizations+which+are+headquartered+in+Turkey%2c+or+are+controlled+by+Turkish+citizens.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eRussian+legislation+defines+criteria+for+%e2%80%9ccontrol%e2%80%9d+in+Articles+5(1)+and+5(2)+of+the+Federal+Law+titled+Order+of+Foreign+Investment+in+Economic+Structures+Strategically+Important+for+State+Defense+and+Security%2c+numbered+57-F3+and+dated+29+April+2008.+Accordingly%2c+persons+are+deemed+to+have+authority+to+control+the+company+or+organization+where+they%3a%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+Hold+more+than+50%25+of+votes+as+shareholders%2c%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+Hold+less+than+50%25+of+votes+as+shareholders%2c+but+control+the+company%e2%80%99s+decision+making+mechanism%2c%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+Are+authorized+to+appoint+the+CEO+or+more+than+half+of+the+executive+body+members+of+the+company+or+organization%2c+or%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+Are+authorized+to+appoint+more+than+half+of+the+board+of+management+or+the+executive+body+without+any+conditions%2c%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eAnother+important+point+is+that+sanctions+in+the+decree+also+cover+Turkish+companies+with+their+headquarters+located+in+Russia.+However%2c+the+Russian+government+failed+to+indicate+the+fields+of+operation+for+companies+which+are+subject+to+these+sanctions.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eAs+for+the+operation+fields+included%2c+The+Resolution+of+the+Government+of+the+Russian+Federation+No.+1457+dated+29+December+2015+approved+the+list+of+certain+types+of+works+which+are+banned+for+performance+in+the+territory+of+the+Russian+Federation+by+organizations+under+the+jurisdiction+of+Turkey+as+well+as+organizations+controlled+by+Turkish+citizens+effective+from+1+January+2016.The+restriction+covers+the+following+operation+fields%3a%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+construction+of+buildings%2c+construction+of+engineering+and+special+construction+works.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+activities+in+the+area+of+architecture+and+engineering+design%2c+technical+testing%2c+research+and+analysis.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+activities+of+travel+agencies+and+other+organization+providing+services+in+the+tourism+sector.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+operation+of+hotels+and+other+places+of+temporary+residence.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+works+and+services+for+the+state+and+municipal+needs.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%e2%80%93+woodwork.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eIt+is+important+to+note+that+here+is+an+exemption+from+this+ban+for+works+(services)+performance+of+which+is+envisaged+by+the+contracts+entered+into+before+the+adoption+of+the+Resolution+of+the+Government+of+Russian+Federation+No.+1457+dated+29+December+2015%2c+for+the+term+of+validity+of+such+contracts.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eEmploying+Turkish+Citizens+Prohibited%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eEmployers+and+contractors+are+prohibited+from+employing+Turkish+citizens+as+of+1+January+2016.+However%2c+Turkish+employees+which+were+already+in+an+employment+or+legal+relationship+with+an+employer+in+Russia+on+31+December+2015+may+continue+to+be+employed.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3e%3cspan+class%3d%5c%22ql-cursor%5c%22%3e%ef%bb%bf%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eThe+Russian+government+created+an+exemption+for+53+companies+to+continue+employing+Turkish+citizens%3a%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%22%2c%22ImageUrl%22%3a%22%2fuploads%2fd6624ba3-7b1c-4004-b93c-e30ca57c0ced.png%22%2c%22ImagePosition%22%3a0%7d%2c%7b%22ID%22%3a%223a2f448d-01ee-4f70-bf39-02498b8dcede%22%2c%22ArticleId%22%3a%221%22%2c%22Title%22%3anull%2c%22Paragraph%22%3a%22%3ch2%3eVisa-Free+Travel+Agreement+Suspended%3c%2fh2%3e%3cp%3eThe+visa-free+travel+agreement+between+Russia+and+Turkey+has+been+suspended+from+1+January+2016.+Previously%2c+Russian+and+Turkish+citizens+could+travel+freely+between+the+two+countries+without+a+visa.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3ch2%3eCharter+Flights+From+Russia+To+Turkey+Banned%3c%2fh2%3e%3cp%3eThe+Russian+government+has+banned+charter+flights+to+Turkey%2c+except+those+used+to+bring+Russian+tourists+from+Turkey+back+to+Russia.+Additionally%2c+supervision+of+regular+commercial+flights+has+increased.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3ch2%3eTourism+Banned%3c%2fh2%3e%3cp%3eRussian+tour+operators+and+tourism+agencies+have+abstained+from+selling+Russian+citizens+tour+packages+to+Turkey.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3ch2%3eTransportation+Prohibited%3c%2fh2%3e%3cp%3eSupervision+has+increased+for+Turkish+sea+transportation+companies+operating+in+the+Sea+of+Azov+and+Black+Sea+ports%2c+as+well+as+companies+involved+in+land+transportation+through+Russia.+The+number+of+trucks+and+lorries+from+Turkey+which+are+accepted+to+pass+through+Russia+is+now+limited.+In+2015%2c+around+8%2c000+trucks+and+lorries+were+accepted+to+pass+through+Russia.+However%2c+this+number+is+set+as+at+a+maximum+of+2%2c000+for+2016.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3ch2%3eJoint+Activities+Suspended+at+Government+Level%3c%2fh2%3e%3cp%3eCommercial+and+economic+activities+between+Turkey+and+Russia+at+the+government+level+have+been+suspended.+However+the+Russian+government+has+appointed+their+Ministry+of+Economy+to+negotiate+with+Turkey+about%3a%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+The+bilateral+Agreement+on+Trade+in+Services+and+Investments%2c%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+The+Middle-term+program+for+economic%2c+trade%2c+scientific%2c+technical+and+cultural+cooperation+for+2016-2019%2c%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Formation+of+the+joint+Fund+for+Financing+Investment+Projects+in+Russia+and+Turkey.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eRussia%e2%80%99s+sanctions+directly+affect+Turkey%2c+Turkish+companies+and+Turkish+citizens.+However%2c+they+also+indirectly+affect+many+European+and+American+companies.+Some+of+these+companies+face+severe+procurement+problems+where+they+have+production+facilities+in+Russia%2c+yet+source+raw+materials+or+parts+required+for+these+facilities+from+Turkey.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eOn+the+other+hand%2c+it+is+positive+that+the+sanctions+exclude+on-going+investment+undertakings+in+Russia%2c+as+well+as+Russia%e2%80%99s+gas+exportation+to+Turkey.+These+are+the+two+largest+goods+and+services+exchanged+between+the+countries.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eIt+is+important+to+note+that+penal+clause+or+compensation+claims+will+inevitably+arise+for+Turkish+and+foreign+parties+which+are+unable+to+fulfill+their+undertakings+and+are+forced+to+cancel+reservations.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eTherefore%2c+serious+and+legitimate+concerns+exist+regarding+the+rights+and+obligations+of+parties+involved+in+agreements+which+are+already+executed+in+Turkey+for+future+expected+businesses+in+Russia%2c+or+agreements+which+would+have+been+executed+in+connection+with+the+on-going+agreements+in+Russia.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eParties+who+are+obliged+to+provide+goods+or+services+are+preparing+to+file+for+objective+impossibility+and+force+majeure+objections.+Meanwhile%2c+parties+which+have+made+a+payment+or+submitted+a+guarantee+letter+are+preparing+for+collection+of+penal+clauses+and+compensation.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eInvestment+arbitration+against+Russia+is+considered+possible+for+investors+whose+long+term+undertakings+are+affected+by+the+sanctions.+Investors+would+be+able+to+seek+penal+and+compensation+amounts+which+they+might+have+to+pay+for+breach+of+these+undertakings.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+Russian+government+%e2%80%93+as+if+acknowledging+the+affects+and+results+of+the+sanctions+which+cause+a+logarithmic+domino+effect+for+governments+and+companies+%e2%80%93+has+given+some+signals+indicating+that+the+sanctions+will+be+eased.+In+this+regard%2c+it+is+speculated+that+the+Russian+Ministry+of+Commerce+is+working+on+draft+legislation+to+ease+the+sanctions.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eConsidering+the+stadiums+and+other+facilities+required+to+be+built+for+the+FIFA+World+Cup+to+be+held+in+Russia+in+2018%2c+Sberbank%e2%80%99s+activities+in+Turkey%2c+Rosatom%e2%80%99s+nuclear+center+in+Turkey%2c+as+well+as+all+other+commercial+projects+and+benefits%2c+the+clear+preference+is+to+lift+the+sanctions+altogether.+However%2c+if+this+cannot+be+done+in+the+near+future%2c+it+is+best+for+both+Turkey+and+Russia+to+ease+these+sanctions+to+keep+the+commercial+effects+at+minimum.%3c%2fp%3e%22%2c%22ImageUrl%22%3a%22%22%2c%22ImagePosition%22%3a0%7d%2c%7b%22ID%22%3a%222e72a8ee-b05d-4bda-82eb-4405e0d8c2f5%22%2c%22ArticleId%22%3a%222%22%2c%22Title%22%3anull%2c%22Paragraph%22%3a%22%3cp%3eThe+Turkish+legislative+regime+for+doctors%e2%80%99+advertising+involves+contradictions+between+provisions+in+primary+and+secondary+legislation.+The+uncertainty+and+legislative+gaps+mean+that+in+practice%2c+government+enforcement+and+interpretation+of+advertising+limitations+are+inconsistent.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+legislative+regime+should+be+updated%2c+to+ensure+predictability+of+government+enforcement%2c+encourage+innovation+by+private+enterprises%2c+as+well+as+keep+pace+with+wider+technological+developments+(particularly+online).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAn+improved+legislative+framework+will+stimulate+and+encourage+financial+investment+in+the+area.+It+will+also+serve+public+interests+because+increased+consistency+and+reliability+of+information+about+doctors+will+ensure+prospective+patients+can+more+confidently+identify+the+most+appropriate+medical+specialist+for+their+personal+ailment.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3e%3cem%3eGeneral+advertising+rules%3c%2fem%3e%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAdvertising+commercial+products+or+services+is+permitted+in+Turkey%2c+provided+the+advertising+contents+are+not+false%2c+misleading%2c+deceptive%2c+or+manipulate+the+consumer%e2%80%99s+will.+Advertisements+containing+exaggeration%2c+which+are+very+encouraging+and+prideful%2c+are+not+necessarily+unlawful.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+in+other+countries+though%2c+Turkish+legislation+restricts+advertisements+for+certain+sensitive+industries+and+subjects.+Such+restrictions+apply+to+Turkey%e2%80%99s+health+sector%2c+prohibiting+promotion+of+many+health-related+products+and+services.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAdvertisements+can+generally+be+categorized+as+either+deceptive+(always+forbidden)+or+non-deceptive.+Non-deceptive+advertisements+include+two+sub-categories%3a+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3epromotional%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+and+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3eattractive%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+advertisements.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3e%3cem%3eContradictory+rules%3c%2fem%3e%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eRestrictions+on+health-related+advertising+in+Turkey+are+not+clear+though.+In+fact%2c+provisions+found+in+separate+pieces+of+legislation+and+ethical+rules+arguably+contradict+each+other.+Viewed+as+a+whole%2c+the+primary+legislation%e2%80%99s+wording+seems+to+be+narrower+than+the+scope+of+information+which+secondary+legislation+considers+acceptable.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Doctors+are+permitted+to+announce+their+clinic%2c+working+hours+and+specialties%2c+but+cannot+make+advertisements+and+announcements+(%3cem%3eArticle+24%2c+Law+No.+1219%3b+Primary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Doctors+and+dentists+are+permitted+to+write+their+name%2c+surname%2c+address%2c+specialty%2c+academic+title+and+examination+times%2fdays+in+newspapers%2c+as+well+as+other+platforms+and+on+prescription+papers+(%3cem%3eArticle+9%2c+Medical+Deontology+Statement%3b+Secondary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Doctors+and+dentists+are+prohibited+from+publishing+thank+you+messages+in+newspapers%2c+or+via+other+means+(%3cem%3eArticle+8%2c+Medical+Deontology+Statement%3b+Secondary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Healthcare+organizations+cannot+make+promotions+(%3cem%3eArticle+29(1)%2c+Regulation+on+Private+Healthcare+Organizations+which+Provide+Outpatient+Diagnosis+and+Treatment%3b+Secondary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e)%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Private+hospitals+can+make+promotions+and+provide+information+which+improves+and+protects+healthcare%2c+as+well+as+inform+the+community+about+the+scope+of+their+current%2ffuture+services.+However%2c+information+which+is+misleading%2c+exaggerated+and+not+scientifically+proven+cannot+be+used+for+promotion+and+providing+information+(%3cem%3eArticle+60(1)%2c+Regulation+on+Private+Hospitals%3b+Secondary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Private+hospital+websites+can+contain+information+about+the+services+offered+by+health+professionals%2c+who+have+the+relevant+knowledge+and+experience.+However%2c+websites+cannot+include+treatment+information+of+any+kind.+(%3cem%3eArticle+60(2)%2c+Regulation+on+Private+Hospitals%3b+Secondary+legislation%3c%2fem%3e).%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Ethical+rules+say+doctors+should+not+(%3cem%3eArticle+11%2c+Turkish+Medical+Association%e2%80%99s+Medical+Ethics+Rules%3c%2fem%3e)%3a%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Advertise+while+practicing+their+profession.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Use+advertisements+for+commercial+means.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Give+a+commercial+appearance+to+their+work.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Act+in+a+misleading+way.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+Cause+panic+among+patients+and+create+unfair+competition+among+colleagues.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAccording+to+legislative+hierarchy+principles%2c+provisions+contained+in+secondary+legislation+carry+less+weight+than+provisions+in+primary+legislation.+Therefore%2c+reconciling+the+contradiction+would+appear+to+be+easy+in+practice.+However%2c+to+ensure+clarity%2c+the+overall+regime+needs+to+be+revised+to+ensure+consistency.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3e%3cem%3ePermitted+advertisements+for+doctors%3c%2fem%3e%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eDoctors+in+Turkey+are+subject+to+the+general+advertising+rules+(above).+A+further+restriction+arises+from+the+Turkish+Medical+Association%e2%80%99s+Medical+Ethics+Rules%2c+which+prohibits+doctors+from+undertaking+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3eattractive%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+advertisements+for+healthcare+services.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eThe+key+difference+between+promotional+and+attractive+advertisement+is+that+the+information+contained+in+promotional+advertisements+represents+the+only+method+of+informing+potential+consumers+about+the+product+or+service.+Promotional+advertisement+falls+short+of+containing+exaggerated%2c+overly+ambitious%2c+incentives+and+appealing+elements.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+%3cem%3ePromotional%3c%2fem%3e%26nbsp%3b%3cem%3eAdvertisements%3c%2fem%3e%26nbsp%3b%e2%80%93+Permitted+advertisements%2c+involving+promotion+of+a+specific+product+or+service%2c+via+general+information%2c+but+avoiding+exaggeration.+For+example%2c+a+doctor%e2%80%99s+statement+that+she+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3ecarried+out+the+first+operation+in+the+country+using+this+technique%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9c%2c+provided+she+actually+did+perform+the+operation+for+the+first+time+in+Turkey+using+that+technique+and+this+fact+is+verifiable.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%e2%80%93+%3cem%3eAttractive+Advertisements%3c%2fem%3e%26nbsp%3b%e2%80%93+Prohibited+advertisements%2c+involving+exaggerated+praise+or+encouragement%2c+as+well+as+seductive+elements+of+the+product+or+service%2c+although+fall+short+of+being+deemed+to+manipulate+the+consumer%e2%80%99s+will.+For+example%2c+a+doctor%e2%80%99s+statement+that+she+is+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3ethe+country%e2%80%99s%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+or+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3ethe+world%e2%80%99s%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+leading+specialist+in+a+specific+medical+field%2c+even+if+disproving+such+claim+is+impossible.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3e%3cem%3eApplying+the+Restrictions+in+Practice%3c%2fem%3e%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eDevelopments+in+medical+science+have+led+to+a+wide+variety+and+depth+of+sub-specialties+emerging%2c+at+ever+smaller+degrees+of+distinction.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eUnder+the+current+regime%2c+doctors+in+Turkey+are+permitted+to+publish+their+qualifications%2c+medical+specialties%2c+and+contact+information.+Such+information+makes+it+easier+for+potential+patients+to+identify+the+most+appropriate+doctor+for+their+illness.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eHowever%2c+under+a+strict+interpretation+of+provisions+in+secondary+legislation+(as+is+usually+adopted+by+Medical+Chambers+in+cities+across+Turkey%2c+as+well+as+by+the+Turkish+Medical+Association)%2c+any+information+going+beyond+these+limited+items+is+technically+prohibited+in+Turkey.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3ePrimary+legislation+clearly+states+that+doctors+can+make+declarations+about+their+expertise%2c+but+cannot+make+advertisements+and+announcements+(%3cem%3eArticle+24%2c+Law+No.+1219%3c%2fem%3e).+However%2c+modern+life%e2%80%99s+ubiquitous+electronic+and+mass+media+combine+to+mean+that+consumers+receive+a+constant+flow+of+information.+%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eTherefore%2c+perhaps+a+more+realistic+interpretation+of+this+legislative+provision+is+that+doctors+can+make+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3epromotional%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+advertisements%2c+provided+the+advertisements+do+not+stray+into+the+%e2%80%9c%3cem%3eattractive%3c%2fem%3e%e2%80%9d+classification.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eUnder+current+practices%2c+regulators+in+Turkey+have+adopted+inconsistent+approaches+to+interpreting+and+applying+the+various+provisions.+The+overall+result+is+that+the+collective+bans+on+certain+types+of+advertising+for+doctors+are+not+always+implemented+in+practice+by+local+Medical+Chambers+or+the+Turkish+Medical+Association.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eFrom+a+commercial+point+of+view%2c+the+uncertain+legislative+framework+and+inconsistent+enforcement+have+a+dampening+effect+for+innovation+by+private+enterprises.+These+businesses+become+less+willing+to+develop+alternative+business+models+or+technology%2c+since+their+efforts+and+investments+may+later+be+deemed+to+violate+the+legislative+framework.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cstrong%3e%3cem%3eThe+way+forward%3c%2fem%3e%3c%2fstrong%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eTurkey%e2%80%99s+approach+to+regulating+health-related+advertising+has+clearly+not+kept+pace+with+developments+in+the+industry%2c+other+legal+systems%2c+nor+with+wider+technological+and+media+advancements.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eProspective+patients+demand+tools+to+simplify+their+search+for+appropriate+medical+specialists.+Counter+intuitively+though%2c+the+trend+towards+simplification+requires+prospective+patients+to+have+access+to+an+increased+volume+and+complexity+of+information+about+candidate+medical+professionals.+Detailed+information+allows+prospective+patients+to+assess+and+compare+medical+professionals%2c+to+ultimately+identify+the+most+appropriate+person+for+their+purposes%2c+based+on+whatever+indicator+the+patient+deems+most+appropriate.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eFor+example%2c+when+comparing+and+selecting+a+doctor+for+a+given+procedure%2c+a+prospective+patient+might+wish+to+know+all+of+the+candidate+doctors%e2%80%99+patient+volumes%2c+track+records+with+that+procedure%2c+surgery+mortality+rate%2c+average+recovery+times%2c+or+even+review+references+from+past+patients.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eHowever%2c+making+such+detailed+information+about+health+professionals+publicly+available+in+Turkey+involves+a+range+of+logistical+and+regulatory+compliance+difficulties.+Logistical+difficulties+will+immediately+arise+in+ensuring+the+information+is+accurate+and+up+to+date.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eMore+notably+though%2c+complying+with+unclear+and+arguably+contradictory+advertising+restrictions+will+complicate+such+a+project+and+discourage+investments.+Without+doubt%2c+publicly+disclosing+detailed+information+about+medical+professionals+will+attract+close+attention+from+local+regulators.%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp%3eAs+a+result%2c+it+seems+that+regulatory+bodies+should+actively+consider+Turkey%e2%80%99s+legislative+regime+for+doctors%e2%80%99+advertisements%2c+in+order+to+update%2c+clarify+and+realign+the+substantive+provisions+to+ensure+they+achieve+their+practical+effects.+Until+this+occurs%2c+health+consumers+in+Turkey+will+face+challenges+in+consistently+and+reliably+accessing+the+level+of+information+they+seek+in+this+respect.%3c%2fp%3e%22%2c%22ImageUrl%22%3a%22%22%2c%22ImagePosition%22%3a0%7d%2c%7b%22ID%22%3a%227cc47507-b27b-4be8-9926-77a0f82784dd%22%2c%22ArticleId%22%3a%223%22%2c%22Title%22%3anull%2c%22Paragraph%22%3a%22%3cp+class%3d%5c%22ql-align-justify%5c%22%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eThe+following+article+gives+a+summary+of+decrees+by+the+Council+of+Ministers+and+communiqu%c3%a9s+by+the+Ministry+of+Economy+regarding+prevention+of+unfair+competition+in+imports%2c+made+between+1+November+2017+and+30+November+2017.%3c%2fspan%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3cp+class%3d%5c%22ql-align-justify%5c%22%3e%3cbr%3e%3c%2fp%3e%3ch2+class%3d%5c%22ql-align-justify%5c%22%3e%3cspan+style%3d%5c%22color%3a+rgb(51%2c+51%2c+51)%3b%5c%22%3eExpiry+Revision+Investigation+Launched+for+Latex